1
00:01:47,458 --> 00:01:52,208
I understand if you're
still in love with Toji.

2
00:01:52,291 --> 00:01:54,625
I'm just glad I'm with you.

3
00:01:54,708 --> 00:01:59,541
[MOMO] Thank you, Kairi,
but isn't it weird

4
00:01:59,625 --> 00:02:02,333
that we planted a peach seed
and got a quince flower?

5
00:02:02,416 --> 00:02:02,875
Huh?

6
00:02:02,958 --> 00:02:04,291
Quince flower.

7
00:02:04,375 --> 00:02:06,166
This looks absolutely nothing
like a peach blossom.

8
00:02:06,250 --> 00:02:08,291
Uh?! Ah!

9
00:02:08,375 --> 00:02:12,875
What?! That man lied to me!
He said it was a peach blossom!

10
00:02:12,958 --> 00:02:14,125
[KAIRI yelps]

11
00:02:14,208 --> 00:02:17,708
[MOMO] Peach Blossom, huh?
I don't think so!

12
00:02:17,791 --> 00:02:20,125
[MOMO laughs]

13
00:02:20,208 --> 00:02:22,208
[KAIRI] I don't need to
plant a peach blossom.

14
00:02:22,291 --> 00:02:25,208
I've got one right here.

15
00:02:25,291 --> 00:02:30,958
Did you know that peach blossoms
have a very special meaning?

16
00:02:31,041 --> 00:02:36,208
They mean "I am your captive."

17
00:02:36,291 --> 00:02:40,208
[MOMO]
I am your captive.

18
00:03:00,416 --> 00:03:03,583
[NORI] Look at those two.
They're never apart.

19
00:03:03,666 --> 00:03:05,375
You think they're dating now?

20
00:03:05,458 --> 00:03:08,083
[AKI] Last time I talked to Momo
she said they were just friends.

21
00:03:08,166 --> 00:03:09,875
[SANGO]
Ah, but guess what I heard?

22
00:03:09,958 --> 00:03:12,416
Someone saw them
kissing the other day.

23
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:13,583
[NORI]
No way!

24
00:03:13,666 --> 00:03:15,083
[AKI, SANGO, NORI growl]

25
00:03:20,375 --> 00:03:22,583
[MOMO]
Uh!

26
00:03:22,666 --> 00:03:24,750
Stay away from Kairi.

27
00:03:24,833 --> 00:03:26,583
[MOMO] Whatever's going
on between me and Kairi

28
00:03:26,666 --> 00:03:28,416
is none of your business.

29
00:03:28,500 --> 00:03:30,833
Everyone at school knows you're
still in love with Toji.

30
00:03:30,916 --> 00:03:34,416
So until you get that out of
your system, leave Kairi alone.

31
00:03:34,500 --> 00:03:35,708
Yeah, he's much
too good of a guy

32
00:03:35,791 --> 00:03:37,333
to be a rebound for
someone like you.

33
00:03:37,416 --> 00:03:39,125
I'm sure anyone would
be good enough for you,

34
00:03:39,208 --> 00:03:41,041
as long as they're
cute and popular.

35
00:03:41,125 --> 00:03:45,500
You better do as we say. Never
talk to Kairi again. You got it?

36
00:03:45,583 --> 00:03:47,791
You poor things.

37
00:03:47,875 --> 00:03:50,708
Kairi would never go out with
someone as shallow as you.

38
00:03:50,791 --> 00:03:52,458
How dare you!

39
00:03:52,541 --> 00:03:53,500
[MOMO gasps]

40
00:03:54,958 --> 00:03:57,541
You have no idea what you're
talking about, you slut!

41
00:03:57,625 --> 00:03:58,791
You don't even love Kairi,

42
00:03:58,875 --> 00:04:00,625
and yet you keep
stringing him along!

43
00:04:00,708 --> 00:04:02,375
Shut up!

44
00:04:02,458 --> 00:04:04,000
[NORI, AKI]
Uh!

45
00:04:04,083 --> 00:04:05,958
Do you honestly believe
that I would kiss someone

46
00:04:06,041 --> 00:04:08,708
I didn't like? Of course
I'm in love with Kairi!

47
00:04:08,791 --> 00:04:10,875
[NORI growls]
You bitch!

48
00:04:10,958 --> 00:04:13,250
[MOMO gasps]

49
00:04:13,333 --> 00:04:16,208
[KAIRI]
All right, that's enough!

50
00:04:16,291 --> 00:04:19,041
[NORI gasps]

51
00:04:19,125 --> 00:04:21,583
You weren't actually gonna
hit my girl were you?

52
00:04:21,666 --> 00:04:22,666
Kairi!

53
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:24,666
[MOMO sighs]

54
00:04:24,750 --> 00:04:27,583
Just because you're not
getting the attention you want,

55
00:04:27,666 --> 00:04:29,666
you treat her like this?

56
00:04:29,750 --> 00:04:32,500
We were just trying to
help you out, I swear.

57
00:04:32,583 --> 00:04:35,500
Go on and get out of here. I'm
disgusted with all three of you.

58
00:04:35,583 --> 00:04:37,958
[SANGO, NORI, AKI whimper]

59
00:04:38,041 --> 00:04:41,500
[SANGO, NORI, AKI cry]

60
00:04:43,666 --> 00:04:46,000
I don't understand
why girls do that.

61
00:04:46,083 --> 00:04:48,083
They smell blood in
the water and attack.

62
00:04:48,166 --> 00:04:49,625
I knew this would happen.

63
00:04:49,708 --> 00:04:53,750
It was just a matter of time
before they started something.

64
00:04:53,833 --> 00:04:56,041
You saved me.

65
00:04:56,125 --> 00:04:58,666
Everything's okay! I'm here!

66
00:04:58,750 --> 00:05:02,916
[KAIRI groans]

67
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:03,625
[splash]

68
00:05:03,708 --> 00:05:05,875
[MOMO laughs]

69
00:05:07,375 --> 00:05:09,250
[MOMO]
It feels so good!

70
00:05:09,333 --> 00:05:11,666
You should come over
and join me, Kairi.

71
00:05:11,750 --> 00:05:14,250
Not gonna happen.

72
00:05:14,333 --> 00:05:15,916
[MOMO]
Aw come on!

73
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,666
You won't even get
your feet wet?

74
00:05:17,750 --> 00:05:19,625
Are you really that
scared of the water?

75
00:05:19,708 --> 00:05:20,750
[KAIRI]
Yup.

76
00:05:20,833 --> 00:05:22,875
That's cool. I guess
that makes sense,

77
00:05:22,958 --> 00:05:25,916
since you almost drowned
in the ocean, right?

78
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,500
[KAIRI]
I don't really remember it,

79
00:05:27,583 --> 00:05:30,916
but from what people have told
me it was a really close call.

80
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,583
[MOMO]
It sure was.

81
00:05:32,666 --> 00:05:35,333
Everyone thought you were
dead when I pulled you out.

82
00:05:35,416 --> 00:05:37,208
I know we've been
over this before,

83
00:05:37,291 --> 00:05:39,541
but are you positive you weren't
the one to give me CPR?

84
00:05:39,625 --> 00:05:41,416
Yes, I'm positive.

85
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:43,750
But I'm curious, how did you
find out that I'm the one

86
00:05:43,833 --> 00:05:45,333
that pulled you
out of the water?

87
00:05:45,416 --> 00:05:47,916
Right after I started going to
school here, I heard your name

88
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:50,000
mentioned in the hallway,
and it sounded familiar.

89
00:05:50,083 --> 00:05:52,500
I remembered that the girl who
saved me had a name like yours,

90
00:05:52,583 --> 00:05:54,833
and since you're the only girl
I've ever known named Momo,

91
00:05:54,916 --> 00:05:56,625
it just made sense
that it was you.

92
00:05:56,708 --> 00:05:57,875
Well if that's the case,

93
00:05:57,958 --> 00:05:59,333
then how come you never
approached me back then?

94
00:05:59,416 --> 00:06:01,541
You'll probably have a hard
time believing this,

95
00:06:01,625 --> 00:06:03,166
but I'm actually
a very shy person

96
00:06:03,250 --> 00:06:04,500
when it comes to
approaching cute girls.

97
00:06:04,583 --> 00:06:07,541
You are such a liar.

98
00:06:07,625 --> 00:06:09,875
It is strange though,
if you think about it.

99
00:06:09,958 --> 00:06:11,500
If you hadn't almost
drowned that day,

100
00:06:11,583 --> 00:06:13,333
we wouldn't be sitting
here right now.

101
00:06:13,416 --> 00:06:15,541
In fact, we probably wouldn't
even know each other.

102
00:06:15,625 --> 00:06:16,916
[KAIRI]
It's pretty weird.

103
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:19,083
[MOMO] So before you
developed this fear of water,

104
00:06:19,166 --> 00:06:21,041
would you have called
yourself a strong swimmer?

105
00:06:21,125 --> 00:06:22,625
Not by a long shot.

106
00:06:22,708 --> 00:06:24,458
Then what in the world
were you thinking,

107
00:06:24,541 --> 00:06:26,750
swimming so far away
from the shore, Kairi?

108
00:06:26,833 --> 00:06:29,541
It was just a couple of
days after the typhoon.

109
00:06:29,625 --> 00:06:32,000
The water was
still pretty rough.

110
00:06:37,250 --> 00:06:40,791
I was trying to kill myself.

111
00:06:40,875 --> 00:06:41,875
[MOMO gasps]

112
00:06:55,041 --> 00:06:58,875
Ha! I totally got you! I was
kidding! I wasn't suicidal!

113
00:06:58,958 --> 00:07:00,541
It was a joke!

114
00:07:00,625 --> 00:07:05,208
[MOMO] A joke? That was
way too serious for a joke.

115
00:07:05,291 --> 00:07:08,541
Maybe this is another side
to Kairi I haven't seen yet.

116
00:07:08,625 --> 00:07:10,291
I mean, it is possible since

117
00:07:10,375 --> 00:07:12,708
I'm always blabbing
about myself to him.

118
00:07:12,791 --> 00:07:14,958
In fact, the more
I think about it,

119
00:07:15,041 --> 00:07:16,750
I barely know anything
intimate about him.

120
00:07:16,833 --> 00:07:19,416
--[KAIRI]  You ready?
--[MOMO] Uh?

121
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:21,208
--[crash]
--[MOMO, KAIRI] Uh?

122
00:07:23,541 --> 00:07:29,791
Ah! Oh thank God!
It still works!

123
00:07:29,875 --> 00:07:33,958
[MOMO] Whoa, Looks like it's
time to get a new case, huh?

124
00:07:34,041 --> 00:07:36,958
I'm a little short on cash right
now, but it's cool though,

125
00:07:37,041 --> 00:07:40,750
I'll just put some tape on it,
and it'll be as good as new.

126
00:07:40,833 --> 00:07:42,458
[MOMO]
That's perfect!

127
00:07:42,541 --> 00:07:44,750
[MOMO]
Crap! I have to start over!

128
00:07:44,833 --> 00:07:48,333
What's wrong with me? Even my
little cousin can knit straight!

129
00:07:48,416 --> 00:07:53,583
I'm gonna run out of yarn soon.
I can't wait to see his face

130
00:07:53,666 --> 00:07:55,625
light up when I
give this to him.

131
00:07:55,708 --> 00:07:58,291
[MOMO]
No! Not again!

132
00:08:01,541 --> 00:08:04,416
[MOMO] I can't believe I
worked on that all night.

133
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:06,750
I'm so tired.

134
00:08:08,833 --> 00:08:11,250
Is anyone in here?

135
00:08:11,333 --> 00:08:14,833
Nurse Misao won't mind if I
take a quick nap before class.

136
00:08:17,666 --> 00:08:23,375
[door opens, foot steps]

137
00:08:23,458 --> 00:08:27,666
[MOMO]
Mm? Mm. What time is it?

138
00:08:33,750 --> 00:08:37,666
[MISAO groans]
Sixty-three kilos.

139
00:08:37,750 --> 00:08:40,625
[MOMO] Oh no! Whatever
you do, don't laugh!

140
00:08:40,708 --> 00:08:43,875
Damn it! I might as well be
pregnant with this belly!

141
00:08:43,958 --> 00:08:44,791
[MOMO giggles]

142
00:08:44,875 --> 00:08:46,208
[MISAO gasps]

143
00:08:48,375 --> 00:08:50,791
Hi. I didn't know
you were here, Momo.

144
00:08:50,875 --> 00:08:56,000
[MOMO] Uh! I'm so sorry!
I didn't mean to laugh at you.

145
00:08:56,083 --> 00:08:56,958
[MOMO]
Uh?

146
00:08:57,041 --> 00:08:58,416
Here's some tea.

147
00:08:58,500 --> 00:09:02,291
Just promise you won't utter
a word of this to anyone.

148
00:09:02,375 --> 00:09:03,875
[MOMO]
That's nice of her.

149
00:09:03,958 --> 00:09:06,375
If I were in her shoes and heard
some kid laughing at my weight,

150
00:09:06,458 --> 00:09:08,666
I'd probably end up
punching their lights out.

151
00:09:08,750 --> 00:09:11,708
Hey Momo! Heard you cut class!

152
00:09:11,791 --> 00:09:13,375
No I was just napping in here.

153
00:09:13,458 --> 00:09:14,833
I didn't get much
sleep last night.

154
00:09:14,916 --> 00:09:16,583
What are you drinking?
It looks good.

155
00:09:16,666 --> 00:09:18,833
Come on, give me a sip. Please!

156
00:09:18,916 --> 00:09:20,041
Quit it!

157
00:09:20,125 --> 00:09:22,250
Don't you have a class
to go to or something?

158
00:09:22,333 --> 00:09:24,083
[KAIRI]
This is way more important.

159
00:09:24,166 --> 00:09:26,333
I'm spending quality
time with my girl.

160
00:09:26,416 --> 00:09:27,916
[MISAO]
Oh yeah?

161
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,500
[MISAO]
Get back here!

162
00:09:29,583 --> 00:09:32,208
Before I give you a valid reason
to be at the nurses' office!

163
00:09:32,291 --> 00:09:33,291
[MOMO laughs]

164
00:09:33,375 --> 00:09:35,000
--[KAIRI] Come on, stop!
--[MISAO growls]

165
00:09:35,083 --> 00:09:37,041
[KAIRI]
Momo, help!

166
00:09:37,125 --> 00:09:40,291
Uh. I can't believe
you're still wearing that.

167
00:09:40,375 --> 00:09:42,041
[MISAO gasps]

168
00:09:42,125 --> 00:09:45,541
[KAIRI] Especially after
what he did to you.

169
00:09:45,625 --> 00:09:47,625
[MOMO]
Uh...

170
00:09:47,708 --> 00:09:48,666
[MOMO]
Kairi!

171
00:09:52,958 --> 00:09:55,958
Kairi, tell me what
happened with Nurse Misao.

172
00:09:56,041 --> 00:09:57,250
Whatever you said back there

173
00:09:57,333 --> 00:09:58,875
seemed to really
hurt her feelings.

174
00:09:58,958 --> 00:10:01,000
Do you know something about
her that no one else does?

175
00:10:01,083 --> 00:10:04,208
Kairi, wait!

176
00:10:04,291 --> 00:10:07,791
My brother, Ryo,
broke her heart. Okay?

177
00:10:07,875 --> 00:10:11,125
Wait a second. Nurse Misao used
to go out with your brother?

178
00:10:11,208 --> 00:10:12,500
When was this?

179
00:10:12,583 --> 00:10:15,166
They went out together
while they were in college.

180
00:10:15,250 --> 00:10:16,416
I needed some help with school,

181
00:10:16,500 --> 00:10:18,333
so she became my tutor
in junior high.

182
00:10:18,416 --> 00:10:19,666
[MOMO gasps]

183
00:10:19,750 --> 00:10:21,541
[MOMO]
Your brother and the nurse?

184
00:10:21,625 --> 00:10:23,375
Why didn't you ever tell me?

185
00:10:23,458 --> 00:10:25,208
It never came up.

186
00:10:25,291 --> 00:10:27,625
[MOMO] Then why keep
it a secret from me?

187
00:10:27,708 --> 00:10:30,125
It wasn't like I was
keeping it from you.

188
00:10:30,208 --> 00:10:34,541
It's just that when we talk,
it's usually all about you.

189
00:10:34,625 --> 00:10:36,833
See ya around.

190
00:10:39,708 --> 00:10:43,750
[MISAO] He always acts like that
when it comes to his brother.

191
00:10:43,833 --> 00:10:45,916
I think he has a complex.

192
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,666
You should've seen
him when I first met him.

193
00:10:47,750 --> 00:10:51,208
He's an angel now compared
to how he used to be.

194
00:10:51,291 --> 00:10:52,458
Maybe it was his way

195
00:10:52,541 --> 00:10:54,750
of rebelling against an
over-achieving brother.

196
00:10:54,833 --> 00:10:56,291
He ran away from
home a few times,

197
00:10:56,375 --> 00:10:58,958
and would skip class constantly.

198
00:10:59,041 --> 00:11:00,666
I think his brother grew
concerned about him

199
00:11:00,750 --> 00:11:02,000
as time went on,

200
00:11:02,083 --> 00:11:05,083
so that's when he asked
me to start tutoring him.

201
00:11:05,166 --> 00:11:06,833
[MOMO]
Tell me about his brother.

202
00:11:06,916 --> 00:11:08,583
You know, what's he like?

203
00:11:08,666 --> 00:11:10,750
He was wonderful.

204
00:11:10,833 --> 00:11:13,416
He has an amazing spirit, and
being with him makes you ask

205
00:11:13,500 --> 00:11:15,833
how anyone could
be born so blessed.

206
00:11:15,916 --> 00:11:17,916
[foot steps]

207
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,791
[STUDENT]
Nurse! Come quick.

208
00:11:19,875 --> 00:11:22,250
Someone just got hit in
the face with the softball!

209
00:11:22,333 --> 00:11:25,833
[MISAO] Be right there! I gotta
go. I'll talk to you later.

210
00:11:25,916 --> 00:11:27,875
[foot steps]

211
00:11:27,958 --> 00:11:29,875
[MOMO]
I guess I was right.

212
00:11:29,958 --> 00:11:32,916
I barely know anything
personal about him.

213
00:11:34,958 --> 00:11:36,791
[MOMO]
That's Kairi's.

214
00:11:43,916 --> 00:11:46,208
[MOMO]
He looks so happy.

215
00:11:46,291 --> 00:11:50,291
Who's this girl next to him?

216
00:11:50,375 --> 00:11:53,875
The picture's so faded,
I can't tell how old it is.

217
00:12:06,875 --> 00:12:08,208
[KAIRI]
Uh?

218
00:12:14,208 --> 00:12:16,333
[MOMO]
So, who's that girl?

219
00:12:21,666 --> 00:12:24,291
I take it you looked
at the photo inside.

220
00:12:24,375 --> 00:12:27,208
[MOMO] There's something
I need to ask you.

221
00:12:27,291 --> 00:12:30,666
Are you seeing someone that
you haven't told me about?

222
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:33,750
Don't worry about it Momo.
It was a long time ago.

223
00:12:33,833 --> 00:12:36,041
Look I'm throwing
it away right now.

224
00:12:36,125 --> 00:12:38,750
You see? You satisfied now?

225
00:13:02,458 --> 00:13:04,875
[tires squeal]

226
00:13:07,250 --> 00:13:08,041
[GIRL]
Kairi?

227
00:13:08,125 --> 00:13:09,208
[KAIRI]
Uh?

228
00:13:13,708 --> 00:13:17,000
[MOMO]
Uh! Its that necklace!

229
00:13:26,791 --> 00:13:29,083
I don't believe it! It is you!

230
00:13:29,166 --> 00:13:33,583
You look so handsome.
I almost didn't recognize you.

231
00:13:33,666 --> 00:13:35,500
Morika?

232
00:13:35,583 --> 00:13:36,833
--[MORIKA]  Come on!
--[KAIRI] Ah!

233
00:13:36,916 --> 00:13:38,416
[MORIKA] Don't tell me
you don't remember

234
00:13:38,500 --> 00:13:40,500
your long, lost girlfriend.
How could you forget me,

235
00:13:40,583 --> 00:13:42,916
with all the crazy things
we've been through?

236
00:13:46,125 --> 00:13:49,291
You know I still have two feet.
I didn't need a ride.

237
00:13:49,375 --> 00:13:51,541
Don't worry about it.
It's my pleasure.

238
00:13:51,625 --> 00:13:53,583
[MOMO seething]

239
00:13:53,666 --> 00:13:56,625
[MOMO] Why is Kairi
sitting next to her?

240
00:13:56,708 --> 00:13:59,250
[KAIRI] Is it hot in here,
or is it just me?

241
00:13:59,333 --> 00:14:00,333
So you've changed.

242
00:14:00,416 --> 00:14:02,375
