245
00:14:11,541 --> 00:14:12,833
[MOMO]
Hm.

246
00:14:16,416 --> 00:14:18,208
[MOMO]
What a cow.

247
00:14:19,666 --> 00:14:22,125
[MOMO]
Thanks for the ride.

248
00:14:22,208 --> 00:14:24,333
[KAIRI]
I'll get out here, too.

249
00:14:24,416 --> 00:14:25,791
[MORIKA chuckles]

250
00:14:25,875 --> 00:14:28,708
[engine revs]

251
00:14:30,916 --> 00:14:34,833
I was almost out the door, Mo!
What do you think you're doing?!

252
00:14:34,916 --> 00:14:36,500
[MORIKA]
Calm down.

253
00:14:36,583 --> 00:14:38,500
[KAIRI]
I can't calm down!

254
00:14:38,583 --> 00:14:39,916
[MOMO]
Uh!

255
00:14:40,958 --> 00:14:42,833
[MORIKA]
You're not mad at me, are you?

256
00:14:42,916 --> 00:14:44,958
Turn around and take
me back to Momo.

257
00:14:45,041 --> 00:14:47,583
Oh, so I see you for the first
time in years and you already

258
00:14:47,666 --> 00:14:50,666
