That's how you treat me?

259
00:14:50,750 --> 00:14:52,625
[KAIRI] Don't you have
somewhere to be right now?

260
00:14:52,708 --> 00:14:57,666
[MORIKA]
Uh. You really have matured.

261
00:14:57,750 --> 00:14:59,708
If I had known you
would end up like this,

262
00:14:59,791 --> 00:15:01,375
I never would have
broken up with you.

263
00:15:01,458 --> 00:15:02,375
