I've been thinking
about us a lot lately,

268
00:15:12,500 --> 00:15:14,625
and how you used to
be so sweet to me.

269
00:15:14,708 --> 00:15:16,833
I know it's been a long time
since we broke up,

270
00:15:16,916 --> 00:15:18,875
but of all the guys I've
been with since then,

271
00:15:18,958 --> 00:15:21,291
none of them have
been a nice as you.

272
00:15:21,375 --> 00:15:23,333
It makes me wonder why
I even broke up with you

273
00:15:23,416 --> 00:15:24,625
in the first place.

274
00:15:24,708 --> 00:15:26,291
It's nice hearin'
you say all this,

275
00:15:26,375 --> 00:15:29,291
but what are you doing still
wearing that necklace?

276
00:15:29,375 --> 00:15:31,750
My brother gave
that to you, didn't he?

277
00:15:31,833 --> 00:15:33,041
[KAIRI gasps]

278
00:15:33,125 --> 00:15:35,375
Kairi.

279
00:15:35,458 --> 00:15:36,875
--[phone rings]
--[KAIRI] Hold on.

280
00:15:36,958 --> 00:15:39,833
[MORIKA] Nice cell phone case.
It's about to fall apart.

281
00:15:39,916 --> 00:15:41,208
Well it'll have to do

282
00:15:41,291 --> 00:15:45,083
because I don't have enough
money to buy a new one.

283
00:15:45,166 --> 00:15:48,083
[KAIRI sighs]
I'm in trouble.

284
00:15:48,166 --> 00:15:50,458
[MORIKA]
Kairi! Where you going?!

285
00:15:53,958 --> 00:15:58,750
[KAIRI]
I am so sorry about that, Momo.

286
00:15:58,833 --> 00:16:02,791
Was that her? From the picture?

287
00:16:02,875 --> 00:16:04,625
Figures. Lemme guess,

288
00:16:04,708 --> 00:16:07,625
you're into that whole blonde
haired bimbo look too, huh?

289
00:16:07,708 --> 00:16:09,875
You must be feeling pretty
good about yourself right now.

290
00:16:09,958 --> 00:16:11,416
Seeing how happy
she was to see you

291
00:16:11,500 --> 00:16:13,125
