had a really ugly breakup,

299
00:16:34,958 --> 00:16:37,291
and I still have some
baggage left over from it.

300
00:16:37,375 --> 00:16:38,916
An ugly breakup?

301
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:41,666
Yeah, my brother
stole her from me.

302
00:16:41,750 --> 00:16:44,250
But after seeing her
today, I realized that...

303
00:16:44,333 --> 00:16:46,916
The baggage isn't really
about feeling like a loser

304
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:48,250
because she dumped me.

305
00:16:48,333 --> 00:16:51,208
It's just the resentment I
have towards my brother.

306
00:16:51,291 --> 00:16:52,500
So there's no
need to worry

307
00:16:52,583 --> 00:16:54,791
about me running off
with my ex, okay?

308
00:16:54,875 --> 00:16:55,958
Really?

309
00:16:56,041 --> 00:16:57,250
[KAIRI]
Yes, really.

310
00:16:57,333 --> 00:17:00,833
You wouldn't lie to me.
Would you?

311
00:17:00,916 --> 00:17:02,000
[KAIRI chuckles]

312
00:17:08,416 --> 00:17:13,708
[MOMO] When did I start
loving Kairi so much?

313
00:17:13,791 --> 00:17:20,375
I don't mind. Kairi won't
hurt me. He never has.

314
00:17:20,458 --> 00:17:23,625
I'm going to trust
him unconditionally.

315
00:17:23,708 --> 00:17:26,208
I'm the one he's with now.

316
00:17:27,666 --> 00:17:29,833
[KAKO]
Wow! That looks great!

317
00:17:29,916 --> 00:17:31,625
I love the color you went with.

318
00:17:31,708 --> 00:17:33,625
So when are you
gonna give it to him?

319
00:17:33,708 --> 00:17:36,375
Probably tomorrow.
He has no idea he's getting it.

320
00:17:36,458 --> 00:17:38,541
It's so cute. Great job Momo!

321
00:17:38,625 --> 00:17:40,541
You could make a fortune
selling those at school,

322
00:17:40,625 --> 00:17:41,750
if you wanted to.

323
00:17:41,833 --> 00:17:43,708
[horn honks]

324
00:17:43,791 --> 00:17:45,208
[ALL]
Uh?

325
00:17:47,833 --> 00:17:49,833
[MOMO]
Uh?

326
00:17:49,916 --> 00:17:53,000
[KAKO, RITSUKO, NAMI panting]

327
00:17:53,083 --> 00:17:54,458
We need Kairi!

328
00:17:54,541 --> 00:17:56,458
I think he went to
the teacher's office.

329
00:17:56,541 --> 00:17:58,875
That's right! He's the
school monitor today!

330
00:17:58,958 --> 00:18:01,708
Oh, no! Right when
Momo's in trouble!

331
