336
00:18:16,458 --> 00:18:18,291
I just end up looking
like a lobster,

337
00:18:18,375 --> 00:18:20,333
I guess that's the just
price I have to pay

338
00:18:20,416 --> 00:18:22,333
for having such
delicate skin.

339
00:18:22,416 --> 00:18:24,833
It's okay though, I hear
that if you tan too much,

340
00:18:24,916 --> 00:18:27,541
you'll look like a catchers
mitt by the time you're forty.

341
00:18:27,625 --> 00:18:29,291
Speaking of, you might
wanna consider

342
00:18:29,375 --> 00:18:33,375
rolling up your window
before your face starts to burn.

343
00:18:33,458 --> 00:18:34,791
[MOMO]
Gimme a break.

344
00:18:34,875 --> 00:18:37,916
