stomach as an ashtray.

349
00:18:49,500 --> 00:18:52,208
We must have laughed
about that for hours.

350
00:18:52,291 --> 00:18:54,458
[MOMO]
Kairi has a scar?

351
00:18:54,541 --> 00:18:57,166
No way! Don't tell me that
pervert hasn't shown you

352
00:18:57,250 --> 00:19:00,583
