372
00:19:46,500 --> 00:19:48,583
[KAKO, NAMI, RITSUKO cheer]

373
00:19:49,708 --> 00:19:50,666
[MOMO]
Mm.

374
00:19:59,625 --> 00:20:02,458
[MOMO] I'm done! I'm done!
I'm finally done!

375
00:20:02,541 --> 00:20:11,625
Now, I just have to wrap it. Ah.
I can't wait to give it to him.

376
00:20:11,708 --> 00:20:12,750
[MOMO]
Yes!

377
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:17,416
[PHONE VOICE]
We're sorry.

378
00:20:17,500 --> 00:20:19,333
The number you have dialed
is out of service or no longer

379
00:20:19,416 --> 00:20:21,833
