the number and try again.

380
00:20:21,916 --> 00:20:27,958
Man. I guess I can try
his home number instead.

381
00:20:28,041 --> 00:20:29,625
[MAN]
Hello?

382
00:20:29,708 --> 00:20:31,041
[MOMO]
Kairi!

383
00:20:31,125 --> 00:20:32,833
I wanted to give you something
tonight, so could you

