420
00:22:20,208 --> 00:22:21,250
[KAIRI]
Uh.

421
00:24:07,500 --> 00:24:09,875
[MOMO] I can't believe how
stupid Kairi's been lately.

422
00:24:09,958 --> 00:24:11,750
